Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:30.32,INlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:34.63,INlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是閃閃發光的黑白怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:37.45,INlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}迷失在假想世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富樫同學你這是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道漆黑烈焰使墮入暗黑世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉  過去的習慣一不小心又回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者跟邪王真眼是由戀人契約相連的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這又算什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快撒鹽  樟葉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36}注：日本傳統觀念中「鹽」有淨化、祛靈的作用，\N在客人走後說「撒鹽」則意指再也不想見到這位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來哥哥你們不是不睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了  這也是魔法魔王少女的陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有  本來就是我們睡著了的不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀杏高中遠東魔術午睡結社之夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對陣紅葉丘高中Siesta同好會的練習比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:17:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不覺得能贏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算現在都不知道她們是不是醒著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們毫無疑問是夢中世界的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前說好了輸了你們就解散
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望濫用午睡部這名字的社團
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少一個是一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼想都贏不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都睡得飽飽的  皮膚光溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還能做的只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在道歉的話說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個社團也不是那麼隨便的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次遇見六花的時候我就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說我們真正的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探查不可視境界線
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是活動不僅限於此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我們的結社
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時我就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟六花你們一起就能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方可是個中二病哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  但是總感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然大家總不被理解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是卻認真努力著  這些跟午睡部很像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠東魔術午睡結社之夏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力地午睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力地玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力地Vanishment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆裂吧  現實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崩斷吧  神經
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(620,656)}Vanishment  this  world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧  這個世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個睡夢世界是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我滾出去
