Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿瓦隆粉碎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Mjolnir  Hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷霆戰錘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去資格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(680,656)}Dark·Flame  Master
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃漆黑烈焰使
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被漆黑烈焰吞噬…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去資格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去資格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩人
