Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Destiny  Ring
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命運之環
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你擁有著如此強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認真起來的話  都可以君臨天下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要守護那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Sleeper's  Wake
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉睡者的覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香學姐  茴香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富樫君  你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了哦  我們贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香  感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎  睡同學她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了  說是自己完敗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們不用解散了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:21:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然  明天還要跟冒牌大人一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡著的時候  做了個很有趣的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼樣的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放此力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Lightning  Blast
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷電爆裂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了這個  雷屬性的技能也完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要玩  凸守也要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年級的  你又在我衣服上動手腳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了啊  冒牌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是和什麼都搭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別多事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少東張西望的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是什麼都沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全也不午睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是能在這裡睡覺是我現在最幸福的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.47,0:21:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太  危險
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.19,0:22:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要幹啥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.12,0:22:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凸守  雷電
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好聽別人說話
